Package com.intellij.openapi.editor.impl

Class EditorDocumentPriorities

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.intellij.openapi.editor.impl.EditorDocumentPriorities

  • public class EditorDocumentPriorities
extends java.lang.Object
    Document listeners are sorted according PrioritizedDocumentListener.getPriority(). (the smaller the priority value the sooner the listener will be called) Some standard priorities are listed here.
